457
00:30:10,760 --> 00:30:12,270
Takže....

458
00:30:12,310 --> 00:30:13,950
Prezidentka....

459
00:30:14,210 --> 00:30:16,530
Nevykládejte si to špatně.

460
00:30:16,650 --> 00:30:19,960
